{"tid":244782,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]係高速係咪唔可以停車？","createTime":"2017-05-15T16:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T05:56:38.000Z","uid":80533,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2cd5a780d3e058cac71d386827e5ed68d10ce0","tid":244782,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"話說我係高速行緊慢線<br />\n點知前面有架拖車停左係度<br />\n我減速打燈想轉去右線<br />\n點知俾後車快過我抽頭走左先<br />\n結果我就出唔到停左係拖車後面<br />\n之後等左成分鐘都出唔到<br />\n架拖車仲走埋，咁我就行返慢線走<br />\n之後架拖車又再停<br />\n我就快快手轉右線走人<br />\n<br />\n之後同人傾呢單野<br />\n俾人話我做錯哂<br />\n係高速唔應該停車<br />\n因為無司機會預測到高速（非路肩）會無啦啦有車停係度<br />\n所以我唔應該減速，應該直接撞上去？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我問返條友咁我應該點做至啱<br />\n條友答我唔應該上高速 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗諗下可能真係佢啱，地球真係好危險，返火星可以任我點揸都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa828b73293a924c751b09b0a96929130ff91960","tid":244782,"uid":64443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"highway停車點都要打死火燈 <br />\n你前車有無打先？<br />\n如果佢一早打左你又唔cut係你無留意"},{"pid":"912fdde37057e2c99fd6451526e85dfa5299238b","tid":244782,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"你反應咁柒慢，揸單車就差唔多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此post 已完"},{"pid":"0097fc6c3d872f8bf4fbf3f0187dda00f848c027","tid":244782,"uid":64443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你反應咁柒慢，揸單車就差唔多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=