t 已完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP牌咋，累積緊路面經驗，多多包涵啦Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d29b7456c0e4bd2249169f818213cb8345b5fbe","tid":244782,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>highway停車點都要打死火燈 <br />\n你前車有無打先？<br />\n如果佢一早打左你又唔cut係你無留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想轉線個時有打燈<br />\n停低有打死火燈<br />\n<br />\n前面無車，係行行下先見到架拖車停低左</blockquote><br />\n你真心唔好揸車，咪害途人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490385eb062c3898dfba3cdd98e90db4675a9b80","tid":244782,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你反應咁柒慢，揸單車就差唔多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此post 已完</blockquote><br />\n同埋唸下靜止停車起步cut去右線要幾耐<br />\n無人會想等你慢慢起步 除非你果部係super car</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次轉線會快手d，第一次係高速停左淆底了<br />\n多謝Ching"},{"pid":"ec775a77af918ffad9621b744632cb52010abfd0","tid":244782,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"cut線就俾油啦 收油先cut線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哄到好埋先見到前面停左咩"},{"pid":"5c3f1314ecf2de5877f0cbef510df62f3909320b","tid":244782,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>highway停車點都要打死火燈 <br />\n你前車有無打先？<br />\n如果佢一早打左你又唔cut係你無留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想轉線個時有打燈<br />\n停低有打死火燈<br />\n<br />\n前面無車，係行行下先見到架拖車停低左</blockquote><br />\n你真心唔好揸車，咪害途人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有彩有3保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a